{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5b7a8774-b542-4514-abe8-daf4d20c2f75","content":"There's no `SettingsPage.xaml` in the working directory, so I'll provide the conversion guidance directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` root element pointing at your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout>\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Slider Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe only change needed is adding the `xmlns:vm` namespace and `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"`. Your existing `{Binding ...}` expressions stay the same — the compiler now resolves them against the declared type.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Emit warnings for broken bindings -->\n  <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nAnd to **promote** those warnings to errors so the build fails:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <WarningsAsErrors>$(WarningsAsErrors);XC0045</WarningsAsErrors>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- `x:DataType` enables compile-time validation of property names and types.\n- Misspelling a property (e.g., `{Binding Thme}`) now produces error **XC0045** instead of silently failing at runtime.\n- If you need an untyped binding somewhere (e.g., inside a `DataTemplate` with a different type), use `x:DataType=\"\"` locally to opt out.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"91acf150-de81-4ca3-9091-fe63b42ac59a","outputTokens":516,"requestId":"942C:840A1:13CABD6:1630837:6A066FCA"},"id":"24becce0-5818-476f-8b83-255602ddbbc0","timestamp":"2026-05-15T00:59:00.956Z","parentId":"adf14b5b-1446-43d8-9cd0-d32eddafd251"}
